{"tid":300962,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"不如睇睇如果依家喬布斯仲在生會點？","createTime":"2017-06-28T10:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T01:46:28.000Z","uid":66351,"like":36,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6e2998edb1ecc4e8aa58ff0974cf536117d8f9","tid":300962,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"第一，iphone依舊3.5吋，你要大mon，請移步到ipad區域 (預言仲在生的話100%會講依句：if they wanna watching video on a larger screen, they can buy an ipad to do it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n後果：ipad銷量每年與iphone一樣同步上升，局你買曬兩件野<br />\n<br />\n第二，ios依舊擬物風格，死都唔會聽jony個死基佬老點<br />\n<br />\n第三，scott forstall 一定仲有得做，天才總係難相處，但一定唔會炒佢<br />\n<br />\n第四，iphone6一定永遠係工程機，冇可能量產，SE咁白癡既事都係，所有產品鏡頭都會做平，佢好睇重整體觀感<br />\n<br />\n第五，蘋果都死唔會加入咩棱鏡計劃，記得蘋果好似係最後一批接觸政府同最後一班加入計劃，而時間就正正係基佬上任之後先有，好似係2012年，而2011年就係病逝果年，慢慢參透（喬布斯接受訪問時對app開發者擅自加入監控私人數據一併稱為son of a bitch）<br />\n<br />\n第六，蘋果發佈會唔會俾adobe同ms上場，生前咬到見血咁，點會咁和平，而且仲會不斷同唔同科技公司開火，訴訟案件數量大增（中國國產手機只要似少少即刻被掠一大筆）<br />\n<br />\n第七，apple music同apple watch會叫imusic同iwatch<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後：喬布斯第二次被董事局開除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （一定會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"4bdcb58e17ad094ce9599c94243589d93f3c915a","tid":300962,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:10:55.000Z","msg":"屌柒而家個乜9tim"},{"pid":"8941afb9b21d08d3c9f1bc7b861e26e9f73ff9ee","tid":300962,"uid":66351,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/181240_a3a6df323b11bb6b71cbba0259477af1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F181240_a3a6df323b11bb6b71cbba0259477af1.jpg&h=611d594b&